### Create a new job (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Junior Backend Developer",
  "company": "Awesome Startup",
  "description": "We are looking for a motivated junior backend developer to join our team.",
  "location": "Tel Aviv",
  "type": "full-time",
  "salaryMin": 15000,
  "salaryMax": 22000,
  "requiredSkills": ["Node.js", "TypeScript", "MongoDB"]
}


### Get all jobs (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs


### Get jobs filtered by location (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?location=Tel%20Aviv


### Get single job by id (public)
# Replace <JOB_ID_HERE> with a real id from the jobs list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/691bf03e31ff25f6752be1f4

### Like a job (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/match/like
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "jobId": "691bf03e31ff25f6752be1f4"
}



### Dislike a job (protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/match/dislike
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "jobId": "691bf03e31ff25f6752be1f4"
}


### Get my liked jobs (protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/match/my-likes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

